  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK421">
<l>aṟivaṟṟaṅ kākkuṅ karuvi ceṟuvārkku</l>
<l>muḷḷaḻikka lākā varaṇ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Wisdom is a weapon to ward off destruction it is an inner fortress which enemies cannot destroy.</l>
            </lg>
